{"tid":1991632,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門賭牌重新公開競投ㅤ李偉農：年底推公開諮詢訂定新博彩法","createTime":"2020-04-27T14:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T02:13:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"37ac6136d6d5dc4d163bb533f16ca058ece048d2","tid":1991632,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"立場新聞 by 論盡媒體 <br />\n<br />\n澳門賭牌將於 2022 年 6 月到期，上屆政府曾經表明賭牌將會重新公開競投，社會關注新一屆政府針對賭場重新競投的工作時間表如何。經濟財政司司長李偉農在立法會引介經濟財政範疇施政方針時表示，政府將把握時間研究及跟進娛樂場幸運博彩經營批給重新競投的相關工作，對於賭牌競投、非博彩元素、博企社會責任、博企支持中小微企等，政府的方向是聆聽社會意見，適時推出公開諮詢文本，集思廣益訂定新博彩法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%B3%AD%E7%89%8C%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%AB%B6%E6%8A%95%E1%85%A0%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%89%E8%BE%B2-%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2%E8%A8%82%E5%AE%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E6%B3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25B3%25AD%25E7%2589%258C%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E6%258A%2595%25E1%2585%25A0%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25BE%25B2-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E8%25A8%2582%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=d7510b29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25B3%25AD%25E7%2589%258C%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E6%258A%2595%25E1%2585%25A0%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25BE%25B2-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E8%25A8%2582%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25BD%25